snippet.title: Age of Empires 3 Ultimate Trailer and Intro
snippet.description:
A combination of the AoE 3 intro and theatrical trailer.
Sounds, looks and feels perfect!

If anyone knows the soundtrack from the vid please tell me!

Also, please check out my 'Improvement Mod' for Age of Empires 3 The Asian Dynasties!
https://impmod.blogspot.com
